Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:35.26,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}気づく　目を見開いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.74,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}仄青い混凝土
