Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:16.71,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,150)}我会将你温柔地蚕食殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:21.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
