Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.74,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}这暗蓝色的混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:40.22,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}冰冷地将我包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.68,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}而后将我揽入胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:51.74,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}用你那已经失去灵魂的躯体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.54,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}濒临崩溃的生命
